Method creates an new ComponentInfo object. Besides the object itself the method also creates new persistent properties for every Property object that belongs to the ComponentInfo object.

@param pComponentInfo ComponentInfo object whose attributes and properties will be saved. The parameter must not be null.
@return ComponentInfo object describing the created object in the database. This object is not the same as the one that was passed to the method. The passed ComponentInfo object should not be used any longer since its data was not updated. The method never returns null.
